Revision history for Perinci-CmdLine-Base

0.04     2014-07-18 (SHARYANTO)

         - [Bugfix] don't switch to help on single command program.

         - Add attributes from Perinci::CmdLine: riap_client (was: _pa) and
           riap_client_ars (was: pa_args).

         - Completion fixes.


0.03     2014-07-18 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes.

         - Adjust to Complete::Bash 0.04.


0.02     2014-07-17 (SHARYANTO)

         - Implement shell tab completion (some quirks still remain).

         - Remove unused hook: hook_after_select_subcommand.


0.01     2014-07-16 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release, extracted from Perinci-CmdLine.
